body_html:
The session.run executes a graph. A graph may have any number of input images as part of it's input pipeline. Typically you will use the tf.data.DatasetAPI to define your data input layer as well as decide on appropriate batch sizes for your model.

Folks will probably ask you to post this on something like stackoverflow as this is probably not best asked here :)

body:
The `session.run` executes a graph. A graph may have any number of input images as part of it's input pipeline.  Typically you will use the `tf.data.Dataset`API to define your data input layer as well as decide on appropriate batch sizes for your model.

Folks will probably ask you to post this on something like stackoverflow as this is probably not best asked here :)
